Cynthia M. BLAKE, Appellant-Petitioner,
v.
BOARD OF REVIEW, DEPARTMENT OF LABOR, Respondent-Respondent,
and
Laurel Healthcare, LLC, Respondent. C-776 September Term 2017
080198 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 26, 2018

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002940-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted.
